  "content_html": "<header class=\"page-width page-width--narrow\" >\n            <h1 class=\"article-template__title\" itemprop=\"headline\">Golden tickets.</h1><span class=\"circle-divider caption-with-letter-spacing\" itemprop=\"dateCreated pubdate datePublished\"><time datetime=\"2026-04-10T07:51:08Z\">April 10, 2026</time></span></header><div class=\"article-template__content page-width page-width--narrow rte\" itemprop=\"articleBody\" >\n              <p>Typographic gold in this collection of thirty 1950s Milwaukee bus tickets. The print textures &amp; surprisingly wild palettes did not get unnoticed either.</p>\n<p>These have been kindly sent by <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/transit.tickets\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Transit Tickets</a>, a growing Instagram archive of transport tickets from around the world. <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/transit.tickets\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">A must follow.</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_01.jpg?v=1775807184\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_29.jpg?v=1775807190\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_26.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_18.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_22.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_12.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_14.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_23.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_15.jpg?v=1775807185\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0952/3604/files/Milwaukee_05.jpg?v=1775807186\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"https://cd